## Key Design Decisions

| Aspect | Decision | Rationale |
|--------|----------|-----------|
| **Register Mapping** | ARM r0-r15 → PPC r3-r18 | Keeps ARM registers "live" in PPC GPRs between instructions |
| **Flag Storage** | Flags in PPC CR0 + r19 (CPSR shadow) | Fast conditional branches using native PPC CR |
| **Memory Access** | C helper functions via CTR branch | DS memory map is too complex to inline safely |
| **Block Size** | Max 128 ARM instructions | Balances translation overhead vs. cache pressure |
| **Code Cache** | 16MB mmap'd executable region | Sufficient for Wii's 24MB RAM, flushed on overflow |
| **THUMB** | Fallback stub | Full THUMB JIT would require a second translator |
| **Exception Handling** | C helper delegation | Mode switches require precise state management |

